additionalProperty.name: Ingredients
additionalProperty.value: Alcohol Denat., Butane, Isopropyl Alcohol, Picaridin, Isopropyl Myristate.

additionalProperty.name: Warning
additionalProperty.value: Extremely Flammable. Will irritate the eyes. Avoid contact with eyes. Read safety directions before using. Keep out of reach of children. Do not spray directly on exposed food, water, food preparation areas or food utensils. Do not spray near naked flame or any incandescent material. Do not smoke during use. Avoid inhaling spray mist. Beware: Intentional misuse by deliberately concentrating and inhaling contents can be harmful or fatal. If rash or irritation occurs discontinue use. If poisoning occurs, contact a doctor or Poisons Information Centre. Phone Australia 13 11 26.
